nvcontrol (0.7.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package release
  * Full TUI dashboard with GPU monitoring
  * Digital vibrance, VRR, HDR support
  * Multi-compositor support (KDE, GNOME, Hyprland, Sway)
